DISCRETIONARY APPEALS ALLOWED

95-343. State v. DeVoise. Montgomery County, No. 14701.

Upon consideration of the jurisdictional memoranda filed in this case, the court hereby allows the appeal. The Clerk shall issue an order for the transmittal of the record from the Court of Appeals for Montgomery County, and the parties shall brief this cause in accordance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio.
